<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="content">
  <div class="upload-section">
    <div class="text-center">
      <p>Docflex</p>
      <h1><b>PPT to PDF Converter</b></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="texte">
      <div class="icons">
        <img src="/svg/ppt.svg" alt="word">
        <img src="/svg/right_arrow.svg" alt="arrow">
        <img src="/svg/pdf.svg" alt="pdf">
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        Drag and drop a Microsoft PowerPoint document (PPT or PPTX) to convert to PDF.
      </div>

      <div class="upload-row justify-content-center align-items-start">
        <% if (!downloadLink) { %>
          <form action="/pptToPdf" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data"
            class="form-control upload text-center mb-3 me-3">
            <input id="uploadb" type="file" name="document" accept=".ppt,.pptx" class="form-control mb-2">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-2"><b>Convert to PDF</b></button>
          </form>
        <% } else if (downloadLink) { %>
          <div class="downloadBox conversion-message text-center">
            <p>Conversion Successful!<br>Click below to download your PDF file.</p>
            <a href="<%= downloadLink %>" id="downloadBtn" role="button">
              <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" type="button">Download PDF</button>
            </a>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bottom-text">
      <span>Your files will be securely handled by Docflex servers and deleted unless you sign in to save them.
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i><br>
        By using this service, you agree to the Docflex Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>

<div class="belowtext"><b>4M files uploaded!<br>
    Join millions of users who have successfully converted PDFs using Docflex.</b>
</div>

<div class="instruction">
  <div class="instruction-text">
    <h2>How to convert PowerPoint to PDF files</h2>
    <p>Follow these steps to easily turn Microsoft PowerPoint files into PDFs:</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>1.</b> Click the "Select a file" button above, or drag and drop your PPT document into the drop zone.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>2.</b> Choose the PPT or PPTX file you want to convert to PDF.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>3.</b> Watch as Docflex automatically converts the file for you.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>4.</b> Download your new PDF, or sign in to share it.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
  </div>
  <div class="instruction-img"></div>
</div>

<div class="last">
  <div class="last-heading">
    <h1>Try our free PowerPoint to PDF conversion tool</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="last-box">
    <div class="last-text1">
      <p><b>Convert PowerPoint files to PDF online</b><br>
        Use Docflex online services to convert Microsoft PowerPoint presentations into PDF files.
        The converted file can be downloaded easily, and you can share it with others when you sign in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="last-text2">
      <p><b>Fast PDF conversion of PPT files</b><br>
        Convert your file in seconds and keep your projects moving.
        Drag and drop or upload a PPT or PPTX file to our online tool and watch your file convert into a PDF document.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="last-text3">
      <p><b>Reliable, trusted file conversion</b><br>
        Thanks to the high-quality Docflex PDF tools, your PPT content will look as expected in the
        resulting PDF file, keeping page elements intact.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

